220
00:15:15.372 --> 00:15:18.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Kalıp seninle gösteriye
göz atarız diye düşünmüştüm.

221
00:15:18.334 --> 00:15:20.502  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ailece kaliteli vakit geçirelim.

222
00:15:22.171 --> 00:15:26.592  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Öyleyse seni taşların harika dünyasıyla
tanıştırmama izin ver.

223
00:15:26.675 --> 00:15:28.052  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ben kuzey kanadını alıyorum.

224
00:15:28.135 --> 00:15:29.595  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Sen de güneyi al.
-Tamamdır.

225
00:15:29.678 --> 00:15:32.932  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Jason, sülfürleri de var!
-İşte orada.

226
00:15:34.141 --> 00:15:35.184  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hey çirkin şey!

227
00:15:36.268 --> 00:15:39.229  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Affedersiniz! Sizi daha çirkin biri
sanmıştım da.

228
00:15:39.730 --> 00:15:41.941  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Siz iyisiniz, güzelsiniz.

229
00:15:45.736 --> 00:15:46.570  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sen...

230
00:15:48.364 --> 00:15:49.698  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nereye gittiğine dikkat...

231
00:15:49.782 --> 00:15:54.286  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Steve? Burada ne arıyorsun?
Ve bu da nedir?

232
00:15:54.370 --> 00:15:55.788  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ne? Sen neden...

233
00:15:55.871 --> 00:15:59.750  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
