234
00:16:00.334 --> 00:16:02.294  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Unut gitsin! Ben gidiyorum ucube!

235
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:07.716  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Neler...

236
00:16:09.009 --> 00:16:11.804  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Evet. Bu, taşların
kimyasal karakterlerini gösteriyor.

237
00:16:32.741 --> 00:16:34.618  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
